features.title: Booking Protection Guarantee
features.subtitle: In the unlikely event a Host needs to cancel your booking within 30 days of check-in, we’ll find you a similar or better home, or we’ll refund you.

features.title: Check-In Guarantee
features.subtitle: If you can’t check into your home and the Host cannot resolve the issue, we’ll find you a similar or better home for the length of your original stay, or we’ll refund you.

features.title: Get-What-You-Booked Guarantee
features.subtitle: If at any time during your stay you find your listing isn't as advertised—for example, the refrigerator stops working and your Host can’t easily fix it, or it has fewer bedrooms than listed—you'll have three days to report it and we’ll find you a similar or better home, or we’ll refund you.

features.title: 24-hour Safety Line
features.subtitle: If you ever feel unsafe, you’ll get priority access to specially-trained safety agents, day or night.

Luxury Villa Sol del Mar III. Welcomes you to an unforgettable stay surrounded by elegance and luxury only a couple steps away from the Adriatic Sea.
Villa Sol del Mar III. is truly a magical place and one of a kind property with a breathtaking view of the crystal clear Adriatic sea. Situated in the picturesque, peaceful and small coastal town Slano in Dubrovnik Riviera, only 33 km from the World Heritage site of Dubrovnik.

Villa Sol del Mar III. is a newly built modern Villa which meets even the most sophisticated demands. When contemporary design meets ultimate comfort, tranquility, privacy, pleasure at the stunning location on the brink of the Adriatic Sea, that’s Villa Sol del Mar inviting you to fully enjoy every single moment of your stay.
It’s the third villa of 3 houses on the same property but with separate entrances and complete privacy offering you a pleasant vacation only footsteps away from the clear blue sea. The superb comfort and exclusive feel of this 5 bedroom property reflects how true a vacation on the Adriatic looks like. Mesmerizing views through the villa and natural lights give an outdoor relaxing feel of spending time in the sun for the entire day. This sensational Villa will take you to the world of glorious sunshine, easy and relaxed living by the sea while you sip champagne enveloped in serene vistas breaking from the edge of the infinity pool.
Distributed over 3 levels, villa offers more then 290 square meters and accomodation for 10 guests. On the ground floor you will find fully modern equipped kitchen with all appliances you need to prepare delicious meals with spacious living room.
The living room and kitchen open on to an outside terrace area and infinity pool. Folding glass doors allow the floor to become an open plan , creating an alfresco living environment. On the same floor is a double bedroom with private en suite bathroom and in the coridor is a toilet for common use. Moving to the outside area of the property is a part with dining area and also sun loungers by the pool, it is the place to settle down with a glass of wine, close family and a plate of Dalmatian delicacies.
A spacious staircase will take you to the first floor where you will find 3 fully equipped double bedrooms with king size beds, air condition system and modern designed en suite bathrooms with walk in shower.
Two bedrooms overlooking the beautiful bay where you will enjoy in stunning view when you wake up in the morning.
On the top floor of the Villa is a gorgeous suite with two single beds, en suite bathroom, walk in shower and living room with stunning views on the bay from the top. A large folding glass door allows you to go to bed and wake up facing the sea.
Different levels of space give you the freedom to relax solo and yet as well a opportunity for social atmosphere and your unforgettable vacation moments. The Villa is completely covered with WI-FI and aircondition. Villa has a parking garage and a private entrance. There is a possibility of private mooring so make sure to grab the opportunity to rent a boat and visit beautiful islands. At Villa Sol del Mar III. you are about to collect unique experiences and make ultimate memories because at Villa Sol del Mar III. the horizon is the limit.

Villa offers a private pool, free wireless Internet connection, air conditioning, hair dryers, dishwasher, washing machine, dryer, coffee machine, ice maker, barbecue, SAT TV and basically all the things you would need during your stay.
Baby cot is available and free of charge as other baby equipment on request.
We will be happy to arrange a pickup for you from the Dubrovnik airport. If you need additional housekeeping during your stay, we can offer this service as well.

We have created an additional spectrum of services, which might uplift your villa stay experience.

PRIVATE CHEF
For those who want to take home a special memory and taste of traditional Croatian cuisine our Private local Chef will arrive at Villa and make amazing gastronomic experience and atmosphere with exceptional service.

SPA TREATMENT
Enrich your holiday with private massage at villa swimming pool or villa terrace. Take a little time-out for yourself and treat your body to a massage it deserves while enjoying beautiful sea views.

PRIVATE SPEED BOAT TOUR
If you are interested in renting a speed boat to explore beautiful Elafiti islands and to fully experience the great Adriatic Sea with its unspoiled nature, secluded beaches and caves but also to taste exquisite local gastronomy, we can help organising your magic day on Elafiti islands with private speed boat and skipper.

ACTIVITIES IN SLANO BAY
Slano bay offers you many activities nearby Villa Sol del Mar. If you want to have a fun day you can rent jet skies, boat ,scuba or bike and have an adventure or even find some hiking trails with amazing views of the Adriatic Sea. But if you prefer to spend your day in relaxing atmosphere of the spa you can find it at nearby hotel .

While we have always taken cleaning seriously we have taken additional initiatives to meet rules and guidelines from governmental and health authorities, (such as the use of personal protective equipment, as well as disinfectants that are approved by regulatory authorities). We also offer extra cost transfer from the airport directly to the villa with a large van to make you fell comfortable.
We hope this initiative offers an additional peace of mind to our guests.
We remain at your service for all questions you might have.
